"{\"uid\": \"fiba3x3.com-en-news-2024-coveted-tickets-up-for-grabs-at-fiba-3x3-universality-olympic-qualifying-tournament-1-2024.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"9 Apr 2024    HONG KONG (China) - Paris Olympic dreams will be on the line at the\\u00c2\\u00a0FIBA 3x3 Olympic Qualifying Tournament 1on April 12-14, 2024.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 144, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With one Olympic spot up for grabs from each gender, the stakes are huge in Hong Kong, China - which has hosted several big 3x3 events in recent years.\\u00c2  What's at stake?\\u00c2  The top eight eligible NOCs, including the tournament host, from the FIBA world ranking list, will participate in the first leg of the UOQT with the winner in each gender obtaining a direct spot to Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 528, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 222, \"end\": 231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.737813464539394, \"rank\": 0.3552433852829905, \"text\": \"Hong Kong\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 517, \"end\": 527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.028960778459499e-14, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by FIBA3x3 (@fiba3x3)  \\u00c2  Who is competing?\\u00c2  MEN: Hong Kong, Netherlands, Mongolia, Latvia, Austria, Switzerland, Egypt, New Zealand  WOMEN: Hong Kong, Hungary, Netherlands, Azerbaijan, Poland, Egypt, Mongolia, Chile  Who are the favorites?\\u00c2  These are some of the best teams in the world, but only one will emerge victorious.\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 871, \"entities\": [{\"begin\