dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2522, \"end\": 2528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soraya_Arnelas\", \"score\": 0.995987317357837, \"rank\": 0.004028617889935923, \"text\": \"Soraya\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soraya_Arnelas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soraya_Arnelas\"}, {\"begin\": 2748, \"end\": 2753, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999856573745927, \"rank\": 1.4338399964759008e-05, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He will be a brute in the paint and so too New Zealand's Tai Wynyard, who showed off his physical gifts during the Asia Cup.\\u00c2  A post shared by FIBA3x3 (@fiba3x3)  \\u00c2  Hong Kong, China also can not be discounted and they will need the support of their passionate fans to get them over the line.\\u00c2  In the women's, Azerbaijan have shown glimpses of what they are capable of on the Women's Series while Poland just two years ago won bronze at the Europe Cup to prove their big game credentials.\\u00c2  Chile and Hong Kong, China can not be written off as they will aim to shock the world.\\u00c2  FIBA\\u00c2    Copyright FIBA.\", \"from\": 2800, \"to\": 3406, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2843, \"end\": 2854, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7528091891799347, \"rank\": 0.3235833000070082, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2857, \"end\": 2868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.o